          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A run loop observer can be registered in only one run loop at a time, although it can be added to multiple run loop modes within that run loop.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "rl",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " already contains ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "observer",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "mode",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", this function does nothing.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
